"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-team-gb-britain-australia-paris-usa-b2586857.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Team GBearned its first medal ofParis2024 after Yasmin Harper and Scarlett Mew Jensen claimed diving bronze in dramatic circumstances.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\", \"score\": 0.99999999999784, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scarlett Mew Jensen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scarlett_Mew_Jensen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tricky third round in the women's 3m synchronised event saw the duo plummet down the scoreboard into sixth after scoring 63.90, but they quickly improved with the following dive, scoring 71.10 to claw their way back into fourth.\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Harper and Mew Jensen scored 70.68 in the final round and the battle for bronze was on withAustralianpair Maddison Keeney and Anabelle Smith.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddison_Keeney\", \"score\": 0.9999999320499479, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maddison Keeney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddison_Keeney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddison_Keeney\"}]}